Installation Instructions
-------------------------

To install boef, run
    ./configure
    make
    make install

Certain users without the appropriate flags set in their environment may have
to add these to the ./configure command like so
    ./configure LDFLAGS=-L/usr/local/lib CPPFLAGS=-I/usr/local/include
or add set them in the environment

To compile without certain features, use the --disable-FEATURE syntax
    ./configure --disable-sqlite3
